OL,7,FA can of energy drink was one of
OL,8,Fseveral household objects being used
OL,9,Fto hide Class A drugs by a couple at
OL,10,Ftheir seaside home.
OL,12,FDonal Francis and Jodi Thompson
OL,13,Fconcealed wraps of cocaine, crack
OL,14,Fcocaine and heroin were found
OL,15,Fthroughout their property.
OL,17,FEach one was divided into weights so
OL,18,Fthey could be sold by the pair
OL,19,Fseparately.
