OL,7,FWhen police entered their address in
OL,8,FYork Road, Southend they discovered
OL,9,Fscales covered in white powders as
OL,10,Fwell as a BB gun with metal pellets.
OL,12,FDetectives described the substances as
OL,13,F'dangerous' and 'unregulated' and said
OL,14,Flives would be put at risk by Francis
OL,15,Fand Thompson's operation.
OL,17,FMore than #2,000 of drugs were seized
OL,18,Fby Essex Police resulting in 25g of
OL,19,FClass A drugs being taken off the
OL,20,Fstreets.
