OL,7,FDetective Inspector Yoni Adler, of the
OL,8,FSerious and Organised Crime Unit said,
OL,9,F"It has taken 18 months but we have
OL,10,Ffinally seen both these defendants
OL,11,Fface justice.
OL,13,F"The drugs they were clearly dealing
OL,14,Ffrom their address in Southend are
OL,15,Fdangerous, unregulated substances.
OL,17,F"They threatened the lives of drug
OL,18,Fusers, and fuel a cycle of crime where
OL,19,Fonly Thompson and Francis benefitted
OL,20,Ffrom the profits generated form the
OL,21,Fmisery of others."
