OL,7,FPaper tabs, containing Thompson's
OL,8,Fphone number, were found which
OL,9,Fwould've been used to advertise the
OL,10,Fdrugs.
OL,12,FDespite mobile devices being found in
OL,13,Fthe property containing hundreds of
OL,14,Fmessages connected to the drugs supply
OL,15,Fchain, Francis answered no comment to
OL,16,Fall questions in his interview.
OL,18,FThomson admitted using Class A drugs,
OL,19,Fbut claimed the mobile phone
OL,20,Fassociated with the promotional paper
OL,21,Ftabs was borrowed from a friend.
